snippet.title: Painkiller Hell & Damnation - Release Trailer and Intro Cinematic
snippet.description:
The official release trailer of Painkiller Hell & Damnation, to get you in the mood for demon hunting starting on October 31st 2012.

Pre-Order: http://www.painkillergame.com/where-to-buy
Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/painkillergame
Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/666pkgame
More information: http://www.painkillergame.com

For a detailed trailer of Gameplay and Features, please head over to http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3RQx4__Sg8
